Rule "Bezier Curve"
    Event
        On Global
    Actions
        c = floor(b) * 3
        Chase Global Variable At Rate
            Visible_To: Everyone
            Variable: a
            Destination: a[c] * ((1 - b % 1)^3) + (((a[1 + c] * 3) * 3) * b % 1) * ((1 - b % 1)^2) + ((a[2 + c * 3] * 3) * (b % 1)^2 * (1 - b % 1) + a[3 + c * 3]) * (b % 1) * 3
            Rate: 0.2
            Reevaluation: Visible To Position And Radius
